Accessibility is just becoming an important topic in web design. There are more 
speakers talking about web accessibility, and this is a very good fact! Standards 
like WCAG and applications like ARIA are doing good work. But there’s more in life 
than web applications, we are in the app century! Apps can be designed and 
developed with an accessible approach. Welcome in this talk about designing 
accessible apps! It doesn’t matter if you are an iOS, Android, Swift, Java, C#, 
Windows,.. developer, all the design techniques we are describing are universal 
idea’s that you can implement in each language or system!